node.text:
☀️ The earth has music for those who listen.
 
Werbung  Ad - When I‘m traveling I need my hardware to perform. I work anywhere I go, being in a plane, exploring the vibrant city or lying at the beach. I value anything that pushes my creativity. With @delldeutschland I found a partner who understands my needs. Great storage for all my photos and videos, high end graphics for my professional editing process and a high performing machine with long battery life so I can get things done quickly to go back outside to seek new adventures. Find your passion now.
#GetIntoIt  #IntelEvo #IntelPartner @Inteldeutschland

node.text:
Last year I woke up in a dream.
A dream, that was reality.
2020 is around the corner and this year I‘m really grateful of what I have experienced. I‘ve traveled more than I planned and was able to see some of the most surreal places on this beautiful earth. So happy that my wife @galina90 was always by my side, making these memories with you makes it so much more special. In the next year I‘m looking forward to collect many more moments with you ❤️
In 2020 my plan is to work on more offline & online workshops. I‘ve learned so much during the years and my goal is to teach more people in the creative field.
Since I got some problems with my health already, I need to also focus more on how to live a more healthy live. Food, sports & meditation is on that list.
Reading is also getting more and more important for me. Everything you could possibly learn is written in books, you only need to start to read it.
Of course I also will continue to create art for me and for you, making you happy & smile is what also makes me happy.
What are your plans for 2020?
